          "Rides"
        ],
        "summary": "Confirm Ride Fare",
        "description": "This operation confirms the fare for a ride once the rider has selected their pickup and destination. Required inputs include the rider ID and any additional parameters needed for authentication and application versioning. Upon successful confirmation, the system will return a response indicating the status of the fare confirmation process.",
